# Development Notes:
# 1. Create a Supabase project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Run the SQL schema from database/schema.sql in the SQL editor
# 3. Get your project URL and service role key from Supabase Settings > API
# 4. Generate a secure JWT secret (32+ characters)
# 5. Configure these environment variables in Vercel dashboard
# 6. Test API endpoints at https://app.postdoserx.com/api/auth/me